<div class="sm:flex sm:items-center">
  <div class="sm:flex-auto">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-semibold leading-6 text-gray-900">VIN Decoder Results</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
      Successfully decoded VIN: <span class="font-semibold"><%= @vin_lookup.vin %></span>
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="mt-4 sm:ml-16 sm:mt-0 sm:flex-none">
    <%= link_to "Decode Another VIN", vin_decoder_path, class: "btn-primary" %>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="mt-8">
  <!-- Grid layout for desktop -->
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
    <!-- Results section -->
    <div class="bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Decoded Information</h2>
      
      <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 text-green-800 px-4 py-3 rounded relative mb-4">
        <strong>VIN:</strong> <%= @vin_lookup.vin %>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <% [ "manufacturer", "model", "vehicle_type", "plant", "variant", "version", "year", "serial_number", "check_digit" ].each do |key| %>
          <% if @vin_lookup.decode_result.key?(key) %>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded p-3">
              <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-600 mb-1">
                <%= key.to_s.humanize %>
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-900"><%= @vin_lookup.decode_result[key] %></p>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        <% end %>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">What do these details mean?</h3>
        <div class="text-gray-600 space-y-2 text-sm">
          <p>
            <strong>Manufacturer:</strong> Confirms the vehicle is manufactured by unu GmbH.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Model:</strong> Identifies the specific model of the unu scooter.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Vehicle Type:</strong> Provides the technical classification of the vehicle.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Variant:</strong> Indicates the motor power rating of the scooter.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Version:</strong> Specifies the maximum speed capability of the scooter.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Year:</strong> The model year when the scooter was manufactured.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Plant:</strong> The manufacturing facility where the scooter was produced.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Serial Number:</strong> The unique identifier for this specific scooter.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- VIN Format Information -->
    <div class="bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">unu Scooter 2.x VIN Format</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
        The unu Scooter 2.x VIN follows this format:
      </p>
      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-3 rounded-md mb-4 text-center">
        <code class="font-mono">WUN U2S <span class="text-indigo-600">X</span><span class="text-green-600">Y</span> <span class="text-amber-600">C</span> <span class="text-red-600">Z</span> <span class="text-purple-600">P</span> NNNNNN</code>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4">
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Position Breakdown</h4>
          <ul class="text-gray-600 text-sm space-y-1">
            <li><span class="font-semibold">WUN</span>: Manufacturer code (unu GmbH)</li>
            <li><span class="font-semibold">U2S</span>: Model code (unu Scooter 2.x)</li>
            <li><span class="font-semibold text-indigo-600">X</span>: Motor power variant</li>
            <li><span class="font-semibold text-green-600">Y</span>: Speed version</li>
            <li><span class="font-semibold text-amber-600">C</span>: Check digit</li>
            <li><span class="font-semibold text-red-600">Z</span>: Year of manufacture</li>
            <li><span class="font-semibold text-purple-600">P</span>: Manufacturing plant</li>
            <li><span class="font-semibold">NNNNNN</span>: Serial number</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Possible Values</h4>
          <ul class="text-gray-600 text-sm space-y-2">
            <li><span class="font-semibold text-indigo-600">Motor Power (X)</span>:
              <ul class="ml-4 mt-1">
                <li>2 = 2000W (2kW)</li>
                <li>3 = 3000W (3kW)</li>
                <li>4 = 4000W (4kW)</li>
              </ul>
            </li>
            <li><span class="font-semibold text-green-600">Speed Version (Y)</span>:
              <ul class="ml-4 mt-1">
                <li>A = Version 25 (max. 25 km/h)</li>
                <li>B = Version 45 (max. 45 km/h)</li>
              </ul>
            </li>
            <li><span class="font-semibold text-red-600">Year (Z)</span>:
              <ul class="ml-4 mt-1">
                <li>H = 2017, J = 2018, K = 2019</li>
                <li>L = 2020, M = 2021, N = 2022</li>
                <li>P = 2023, R = 2024, S = 2025</li>
                <li>And so on...</li>
              </ul>
            </li>
            <li><span class="font-semibold text-purple-600">Plant (P)</span>:
              <ul class="ml-4 mt-1">
                <li>Z = Zhuhai, China</li>
              </ul>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs italic mt-4">
        Example: WUNU2S4BXM<span class="text-gray-400">Z000123</span> = 4kW motor, max 45 km/h, built in 2021
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
